{"tid":1103158,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"年度最佳笑話 支那官方宣布 強力遏阻侵犯個資行為","createTime":"2019-04-12T08:13:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-12T08:19:50.000Z","uid":32511,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e422ae6b8890250878fca7139e1aa3dd41a9e46d","tid":1103158,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T08:13:22.000Z","msg":"中國國家市場監管總局近日印發通知，今年4月至9月期間將部署開展「守護消費」暨打擊侵害消費者個人資訊違法行為專項執法行動，重點打擊侵害消費者個人資訊違法行為，營造安全放心消費環境。<br />\n <br />\n本次專項執法行動主要鎖定房產租售、小貸金融、教育培訓、保險經紀、美容健身、裝飾裝修、旅遊住宿、快遞、電話行銷、網站或APP運營等，消費者反應容易違法侵害個資的領域，重點查處未經消費者同意，收集使用消費者個人資訊、洩露出售或者非法向他人提供所收集的消費者個人資訊，以及未經同意發送商業性資訊等違法行為。"},{"pid":"f4a4efe9096c0885b282367a784ce854155dbd0c","tid":1103158,"uid":202496,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T08:15:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cMesAeC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcMesAeC.png&h=3591a570&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"53af7aa5b732368010c67199c6e857d31f8519dc","tid":1103158,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T08:16:22.000Z","msg":"個人資料"},{"pid":"94a100fbd97aae08e7820a1898e73fae5b2a7c82","tid":1103158,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f4a4efe9096c0885b282367a784ce854155dbd0c","tid":1103158,"uid":202496,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T08:15:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cMesAeC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcMesAeC.png&h=3591a570&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T08:18:01.000Z","msg":"但除咗哩樣樓主好正常<br />\n唔覺有打手/五毛行為<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b94319582f13e87195d8985d844eb301035b9304","tid":1103158,"uid":28195,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T08:19:50.000Z","msg":"支那法律不嬲寫得好嚴格，仲對平民好保障，不過執行同寫係兩回事<br />\n<br />\n譚餵豬講陽光司法，亦只指法